  <brief_title>Impacts of Stoppa and Total Extraperitoneal Inguinal Hernia Repair on the Lower Extremity Muscular Functions</brief_title>
  <official_title>Quantitative Assessment of the Impacts of Stoppa Repair and Total Extraperitoneal Repair on the Lower Extremity Muscular Functions in Cases of Unilateral Inguinal Hernia; a Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
