  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of physical activity parameters of the lower extremity muscles in patients who
      received total extraperitoneal repair (TEP) and STOPPA repair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The patients were evaluated during the preoperative period and in the postoperative day 3, to
      achieve an isometric and isokinetic, objective assessment of the pain-related lower extremity
      muscular function changes.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
